Although BERT was probed for {{2307.03122_FO0018||FO}} objects when generating object lists, only {{2307.03122_FO0019||FO}} objects were retained after post-processing. Objects with invalid types occur due to the zero-shot setting. Also, other eminent masked LMs, including BERT-base, RoBERTa-base, and RoBERTa-large, achieve 60.61%, 54.82%, and 58.90% max-F1 scores.